title: Dan Callaghan: I deserved to be the first to leave The Apprentice - Echo-news.co.uk
text:
Dan joined Team Connexus's project manager April Jackson and Brett Butler-Smythe in the boardroom, but was axed for making zero sales in the first task. "Do I think I deserved to stay in the process given my abysmal selling record? No, not at all," the 24-year-old online fragrance retailer admitted.
 Echo-news.co.uk.
